                </div>
                <hr class="line">
            <li><span class="toggle-icon" onclick="toggleAnswer('user3')">I received an error message.</span></li>
                <div class="faq" id="user3">sorry! please take a screenshot and send it to info@batproject.ch . a short description
                    on how and where the error occurred would be helpful.
                </div>
